result.name: Cloud View Chinese BBQ Congee Noodle Restaurant

reviews.text: Food is okay but the fact that people can smoke outside ruins the experience, but service is nice and so are the people
A good local cafe serving the neighborhood/

Decent cha chan teng (茶餐廳) with a wide range of selection from bbq pork to comfort food such as French toast with milk tea. You can stay in the indoor side for air-conditioned dining, or chill out at the foyer for fresh breeze.
A gem for foodies in such a remote location.
Dogs welcome :)

reviews.text:
要大讚走到飲管， 環境舒服。
好鍾意呢度歡迎狗狗～ Dog Friendly～
不過個菠蘿油唔好食😅
價錢不便宜，食物質素一般，只有燒味是能夠接受的，其他食物質素非常差。
Food is okay but the fact that people can smoke outside ruins the experience, but service is nice and so are the people
Hidden gem local 茶餐廳 chill place

西多士，以30蚊黎講，算係我食過最好食
奶茶18蚊，好味
雞粥30蚊，細碗左，雞幾舊仔，唔合格
二點半後有下午茶餐，西多餐32, 等2:30後黎食半好多
